'''Creature Feature''' was a series of web enhancements for the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game|d20]] [[Star Wars]] [[roleplaying game]] on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website, with each article describing a creature and giving it game statistics. Many of these creatures were new, or new variations on old creatures, and the articles were often designed to show creatures associated with a recently released RPG book. Many of the Creature Feature articles were written by [[Jeff Quick]].

